{"tid":186072,"cid":32,"subCid":0,"title":"20至24 Whatsapp Group (第十回)","createTime":"2017-04-04T03:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T17:53:57.000Z","uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd7d32de5909a78ce8113ee90e4a3529f63f085","tid":186072,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"時移世易 20至24 Whatsapp Group 乃 18至22 Whatsapp Group延續。 <br />\n<br />\n我們希望關系和諧，因始沒有你我之分，更沒有兩登之分。<br />\n<br />\n都開左一段日子 係一個有秩序又開心既Group <br />\n<br />\n之前填過既可以在填多次 順便睇睇張Form既聲明及條款細則<br />\n<br />\n張Form會開到4月11日 12am 4月13-16有專人通知入Group 多謝各位一路以來既支持 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n20至24 Whatsapp Group為會員而設，暫時只限相關會員加入。謝謝！。<br />\n<br />\n***為確保言論自由不被惡意功擊/侵犯及Group內成員及相關私穩，閣下填寫表格時，將可能保留IP確保閣下本人同意 聲明及條款細則 所有條款 ，有須要時將作為證供。請注意***<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再次感謝各位一年來的支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"54415128034b1cb716f1103763550260742cd457","tid":186072,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629fa2e22b066d745a654bc4eedcb90e853f5346","tid":186072,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b94d769d92d9814da3d9088f2f805f027b32cf","tid":186072,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6523163aa3c14ba506578a23dcf2c0c32acdd0ad","tid":186072,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026ed69bf65687e68ae28ddb3b3bff016eac7788","tid":186072